Loading Synthea Data

Here we’ll walk through the different data files from the synthea data generator. Synthea can generate data in a number of formats including:

  • CCDA
  • CSV
  • FHIR
  • Text

Reading Text Data

with open('../data/text/Abraham100_Klein929_8ff56a9d-b91c-48c7-a6e9-a55344881a36.txt') as f:
    for idx, line in enumerate(f.readlines()):
        print(f'{idx}: {line}')
        if idx >= 5:
            break
